<p><img data-action="zoom" class="aligncenter" src="http://image.woshipm.com/wp-files/2020/09/45aJcL1V6WBTvqkoBtSv.png" width="900" height="582" /></p>
<p style="text-align: center;">「学员认真学习」</p>
<p><img data-action="zoom" class="aligncenter" src="http://image.woshipm.com/wp-files/2020/09/pomBjk4eKbRF4lRW6gLC.png" width="900" height="510" /></p>
